    <div id="benefits">
        <h1>Benefits</h1>
        <p>Working in any NGO would provide you lots of exposure to the real world. Watching the people with nothing
            will motivate you to do more for yourself and society.<br>
            Working with us would give you working underpressure, leadership qualities and also most importantly, a
            satisfaction you get when you help other people.
            Our World need more kind people, So join us and help the society.</p>
        <img src="hand.png" alt="">
